I used simple two step process 

1) Coloured all the island using Depth FIrst-Search and Store their size in Map
2) Search the Zeros in Matrix and Explore it all four direction and Simply add the island size and store the biggest possible island connected by this "zero" in a variable.

Now return biggest possible island, unless it is zero, else return size of whole matrix. because that means no zero exist.
