First run DFS according to the similar problem largest island,worth noting is the fact that wach 1 would be a part of a particular island and
after running the dfs as per the similar problem we will be able to get the area of the island related to the 1 which belongs to that particular island number .

Then,thereafter just pick each 0 and then search for all the ones in its neighbour,check the island number where these neighbours belong to and the area assciated with that isalnd number,add a 1 to that area and thus find the max.
q?Why are we adding 1 to that max area,coz that particular 0 would finally add up to the area by becoming a 1.

