Example Test Run
    Input: s = "dcab", pairs = [[0,3],[1,2]]

    Step 1, generate disjoint set roots
        [0,1,2,3] => [0,1,2,0] => [0,1,1,0]
    Step 2, group characters by set
        {} => {0:[d]} => {0:[d], 1:[c]} => {0:[d], 1:[c,a]} => {0:[d,b], 1:[c,a]}
    Step3, sort characters within each set
        {0:[d,b], 1:[c,a]} => {0:[b,d],1:[a,c]}
    Step4, generate result string by set and its sorted chars
        'bacd'

Complexity
    Time O(n * a(n) + n * a(n) + n log n + n) => O(n log n)
	Space O(n)

